quran[8{c,v,t}:
18,54,hum ne iss quran mein logon ko terhan terhan se samjhaya magar ensaan bara hi jhagralu waqay howa hai
18,55,"unn ke samnay jab hadaayat aayi to usay maan-ne aur apne rab ke huzoor maffi chahanay se aakhir unn koks cheez ne rok diya? iss ke siwa aur kuch nahi ke woh muntazir hain ke unn ke sath bhi wohi kuch ho jo pichli qomon ke sath ho chuka hai, ya yeh ke woh azaab ko samnay atay dekh len !"
18,56,Rasolo-n ko hum is kaam ke siwa aur kisi gharz ke liye nahi bhaijtay ke woh basharat aur tanbeeh ki khidmat injaam day den magar kafiroon ka haal yeh hai ke woh baatil ke hathyaar le kar haq ko neecha dikhaane ki koshish karte hain aur unhon ne meri ayaat ko aur unn tnbihat ko jo inhen ki gayeen mazaq bana liya hai
18,57,"aur uss shakhs se barh kar zalim aur kon hai jisay is ke rab ki ayaat suna kar nasiyaat ki jaye aur woh unn se mun phairay aur uss buray injaam ko bhool jaye jis ka sir o samaan is ne apne liye khud apne hathon kya hai? ( jin logon ne yeh rawish ikhtiyar ki hai ) un ke dilon par hum ne ghilaaf charha diye hain jo inhen quran ki baat nahi samajhney dete, aur unn ke kaanon mein hum ne gharani peda kar di hai tum inhen hadaayat ki taraf kitna hi bulaao, woh is haalat mein kabhi hadaayat nah payen ge"
18,58,tera rab bara dar guzar karne wala aur Raheem hai woh un ke krtoton par inhen pakarna chahta to jaldi hi azaab bhaij deta magar un ke liye waday ka aik waqt muqarrar hai aur is se bach kar bhaag niklny ki yeh koi raah nah payen ge
18,59,"yeh azaab Raseedah bastiyan tumahray samnay mojood hain unhon ne jab zulm kya to hum ne inhen halaak kar diya, aur un mein se har aik ki halakat ke liye hum ne waqt muqarrar kar rakha tha"
18,60,"( zara inn ko woh qissa sunaaoo jo moose ko paish aaya tha ) jabkay moose ne apne khadim se kaha tha ke"" mein apna safar khatam nah karoon ga jab taq ke dono daryaaon ke sngm par nah poanch jaoon, warna mein aik zamana daraaz taq chalta hi rahon ga """
18,61,pas jab woh un ke sngm par puhanche to apni machhli se ghaafil ho gay aur woh nikal kar is terhan darya mein chali gayi jaisay ke koi surang lagi ho
